9.Sharing Settings and Security

Go to setup >> type Sharing Settings in quick find box >> Click on the Sharing Settings.

Scroll down and find Drop-Off point Sharing Rules.

Click on new near Drop-Off point Sharing Rules and Name it as:

Label: Rule 1
Rule Name: Rule_1
Select your rule type: Select Based on criteria.

Select which records to be shared:

Field: Operator: Value = Distance: less than: 15
Select the users to share with: Near Share With
Public Groups: Iksha

Click on Save.


create same for Rule_2 and Rule_3
